# Secrets / PII gate (config-spec E6 / Mode B) — real values never enter git.
config.json
*.env
!*.env.template
secrets/*
!secrets/README.md
!secrets/.gitkeep
claude.json
.claude.json
*credentials*.json
*.key
*.pem
!*.key.template
!*.pem.template
reports/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.idea/
.DS_Store
NUL
docs/backtest-2026-06/distress_features.json
docs/backtest-2026-06/_*.log
docs/backtest-2026-06/_*.json

# --- Data boundary (Skill Repo Spec v1 s9) ---
# A public skill repo is an UNINITIALIZED TOOL. Real-run output (verdicts, scorecard) is DATA:
# it lives in ~/.small-cap-deepdive-config/data/, resolved by tools/datadir.py. The repo carries
# only the schema. metrics/verdicts.jsonl held real-run verdict rows before the 2026-07 audit --
# not pasted there by anyone, but APPENDED BY THE SKILL, on every run.
metrics/*
!metrics/*.example
